{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"82051b9abd","title":"对中南军区三反指示和谭政来电的复电和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"95951d7abb","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"82051b9abd"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"acfb409325","type":"title","text":"元且祝词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"b975565dad","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们全体——人民政府的工作人员，人民志愿军和人民解放军的指挥员、战斗员，各民主党派，各人民团体，各少数民族和全国人民，在各个工作战线上的胜利！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"1c33176fc2","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在抗美援朝战线上的胜利！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"3e66df7e84","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在国防战线上的胜利！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"9d362c026e","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在土地改革战线上的胜利！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"15281b62ba","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在镇压反革命战线上的胜利！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"7be1b8a9a8","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在经济和财政战线上的胜利","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"311480d1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在文化和教育战线上的胜利！","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"fe8024a5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在社会各界首先是知识分子的思想改造战线上的胜利！","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"6c36bf4b54","type":"paragraph","text":"我还要祝我们在新开辟的一条战线上的胜利，这就是号召我国全体人民和一切工作人员一致起来，大张旗鼓地，雷厉风行地，开展一个大规模的反对贪污、反对浪费、反对官主义的斗争，将这些旧社会遗留下来的污毒洗干净！","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"3fee3c944b","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，我们在上述一切战线上，在一九五一年，都已取得了胜利，有许多是极其伟大的胜利。我们希望，经过我们的共同努力，所有这些工作，在一九五二年能够取得更大的胜利","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"},{"id":"8b9246c5b0","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国方岁！","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd"}],"page":{"id":"b6a405016b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"82051b9abd","start":218,"end":218}}}},"__N_SSG":true}